ISLAMABAD, May 7 (APP): Minister for Information and Broadcasting Marriyum Aurangzeb said on Saturday that today, Khadim-e-Pakistan Shehbaz Sharif would address a public meeting of brave and courageous Pakhtuns in Bisham, Shangla area of Khyber Pakhtunkhwa.
In a tweet, she said Adviser to the Prime Minister and President PML-N Khyber Pakhtunkhwa Engineer Amir Muqam and other party leaders will also address the meeting.
